{"tid":88951,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得生駒里奈同埋達哥既遭遇好相似？","createTime":"2017-01-21T04:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T16:39:33.000Z","uid":16063,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"30a56fb50c64f41bcce216140c2660e54b0d1522","tid":88951,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:14:20.000Z","msg":"明明達哥(生駒)係靠自己既努力，出心出力開台(工作)，先累積到咁多支持者。<br />\n而家竟然比人話係backup佬幫佢backup(sony比center生駒)，達哥(生駒)先有得紅，<br />\n仲要力就達哥(出)，錢就backup佬(sony)袋，<br />\n而家達哥(生駒)只係自己backup番(拎番個center做)，就比人係咁攻擊，<br />\n希望大家可以好好珍惜達哥同生駒，如果冇左達哥同生駒睇既話，我諗香港同日本真係會暴動。"},{"pid":"1afba892a8a12475ca13650628c8415a0cd0305f","tid":88951,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:15:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲要力就達哥(生駒)出，錢就backup佬(sony)袋</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b318de3c9725f6e3e43764236aa3f630330f9677","tid":88951,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:25:35.000Z","msg":"開始分唔到係推定反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3538c014311eb1c7d2dea439287cd6a29d407167","tid":88951,"uid":60229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b47dd4476860eee80422f8e22321a8df1d6e282","tid":88951,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T05:06:41.000Z","msg":"邊個又比負評呀"},{"pid":"55805e795ec6694b9a098ce2fd59ffe051c29d4b","tid":88951,"uid":60229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T05:13:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個又比負評呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你一個我一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acef7ce9d62420f13449d9ec5cfc639eeb1939a8","tid":88951,"uid":16063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:19:03.000Z","msg":"希望大家評下理,幫生駒講番句公道說話。"},{"pid":"3e03c215d4b2c68fa78afa497e3ac0773195fc1f","tid":88951,"uid":60229